4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The 16-week program includes 3 live online classes per week, accommodating up to 16 participants. It covers a foundational understanding of Windows, Linux, network, and server administration while teaching cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Students will learn about risk management and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, graduates receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish.

